					<div class="bio">
						<h4>David S. Brown</h4>
												<p>David S. Brown teaches history at Elizabethtown College in Pennsylvania. He is the author of several books including <em>The Last American Aristocrat</em>; <em>Paradise Lost: A Life of F. Scott Fitzgerald</em>; and <em>Richard Hofstadter: An Intellectual Biography</em>.</p>
